enum TBTDiscoverabilityMode

Enumeration for BT discoverability mode setting This must always match BTServer's TBTServerScanMode enum

Enumerator:
EBTDiscModeHidden  Page enabled, scan disabled.
EBTDiscModeGeneral  Page enabled, scan enabled.
EBTDiscModeTemporary  This value is used to set the device to EBTServerScanModeGeneral temporarily First value after reserved range.
